OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on the collapse
OL,7,Fof a music festival company in Cornwall
OL,9,FMore than #6,000 has been raised to
OL,10,Fsupport "devastated" traders and crew
OL,11,Fmembers who have been left out of
OL,12,Fpocket following the collapse of a
OL,13,Fmusic festival company in Cornwall.
OL,15,FThe organiser of the Morvala festival,
OL,16,Fwhich took place in June on the Mount
OL,17,FEdgcumbe estate, says he was left with
OL,18,F"no option" but to fold the company
OL,19,Fafter suffering huge financial losses.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
