OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,FThe Kernowfornia Festival planned for
OL,7,FLooe in September has been cancelled,
OL,8,Fwith dozens of performers and stage
OL,9,Fcrew going unpaid.
OL,11,FJacob McTighe, who was technical
OL,12,Fproduction manager at Morvala, said:
OL,13,F"Personally, I've missed out on about
OL,14,F#9,500, and my partner #3,500.
OL,16,F"She did the crew catering and I did a
OL,17,Flot of the artist advancing, trying to
OL,18,Fpull the show together within the six-
OL,19,Fweek period before the show happened.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,F"I put a lot of time and effort into
OL,7,Ftrying to make the show happen and
OL,8,Fdidn't receive any remuneration for
OL,9,Fthat.
OL,11,F"I'm absolutely gutted. I poured my
OL,12,Fheart and soul into the event, we all
OL,13,Fbelieved in it, we thought it had legs
OL,14,Fand we thought we'd be doing it every
OL,15,Fyear for at least the next ten years
OL,16,Fbut because of the poor financial
OL,17,Fplanning we were let down and it won't
OL,18,Fbe happening again."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,FThe organiser of the festival, Jon
OL,7,FStafford, said he was left with no
OL,8,Fother option but to liquidate the
OL,9,Fcompany due to huge financial losses.
OL,11,FA Crowdfunder campaign, set up to help
OL,12,Fthose left out of pocket, has so far
OL,13,Fraised more than #6,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,FKathleen Rixon, who organised the
OL,7,FCrowdfunder, said: "The purpose isn't
OL,8,Fnecessarily to resolve what everyone's
OL,9,Flost, that would be impossible, so
OL,10,Fit's more of a platform to show
OL,11,Fsolidarity in the community, to show
OL,12,Fthat the local people who worked all
OL,13,Fthose hours are valued for their work
OL,14,Fand how much people enjoyed the event.
OL,16,F"They pulled off the show, the show
OL,17,Fwas incredible, and loads of people
OL,18,Fcouldn't wait for the next one, so for
OL,19,Fthis all to happen is just devastating
OL,20,Freally."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,FIn a statement, Jon Stafford of
OL,7,FGracenote Promotions Ltd said he is
OL,8,F"deeply and profoundly sorry" to
OL,9,Feveryone who worked so hard to make
OL,10,Fthe festival happen.
OL,12,F"We know many of you placed your trust
OL,13,Fin us," he said.
OL,15,F"Many of you committed months of work,
OL,16,Finvested your own time and resources,
OL,17,Fsupported us through an incredibly
OL,18,Fambitious project and believed in the
OL,19,Fvision we were trying to create.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784884712
OL,3,C'Devastated' crew members left unpaid
OL,4,Cafter Cornwall festival collapse
OL,6,F"The fact that so many of you are now
OL,7,Ffacing financial loss is something
OL,8,Fthat weighs incredibly heavily on us."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
